('11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111', 'aryan', 'aryan@horizon.blog', '$2a$10$dXJ3SW6G7P50lGmMkkmwe.u0v2jvIei6irMIXja2fJGZveHFkNj2a', 'Aryan Mehta', 'Writer at the intersection of science, philosophy, and lived experience. Based in Mumbai. Interested in consciousness, complexity, and the limits of understanding.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500648767791-00dcc994a43e', 'USER', '2025-01-10 09:00:00', '2026-03-12 09:00:00'),
